#: templates/home.html:110
msgid ""
"We place <span class=\"text-gold-custom\">crowns</span> on women, like queens"
msgstr ""
"Nous plaçons des <span class=\"text-gold-custom\">couronnes</span> sur les "
"femmes, comme des reines"

#: templates/home.html:117
msgid "<b>LIONESS</b> is much more than a magazine."
msgstr "<b>LIONESS</b> n'est pas seulement un magazine."

#: templates/home.html:119
msgid ""
"It's a community born in Gabon that shines a spotlight on African and Afro-"
"descendant women, both in Africa and in the diaspora, while remaining open "
"to women worldwide."
msgstr ""
"C’est une communauté née au Gabon, qui met en lumière les femmes africaines "
"et afro-descendantes, en Afrique comme dans la diaspora, tout en restant "
"ouverte aux femmes du monde entier."

#: templates/home.html:121
msgid ""
"We celebrate ambitious, entrepreneurial, creative, and committed women "
"through inspiring stories, authentic journeys, and meaningful content."
msgstr ""
"Nous valorisons des femmes ambitieuses, entrepreneuses, créatives et "
"engagées, à travers des histoires inspirantes, des parcours authentiques et "
"des contenus porteurs de sens."

#: templates/home.html:123
msgid ""
"Joining LIONESS, means joining a movement that celebrates women, their "
"ambitions, and their impact on the world."
msgstr ""
"Rejoindre LIONESS, c’est rejoindre un mouvement qui célèbre les femmes, "
"leurs ambitions et leur impact dans le monde."

#: templates/home.html:125
msgid "See the magazines"
msgstr "Voir les magazines"

#: templates/home.html:139
msgid "A space to inspire, connect, and impact"
msgstr "Un espace pour inspirer, connecter et impacter"

#: templates/home.html:146
msgid ""
"Discover inspiring content on entrepreneurship, culture, leadership, well-"
"being and much more."
msgstr ""
"Découvrez du contenu inspirant sur l'entrepreneuriat, la culture, le "
"leadership, le bien-être et bien plus encore."

#: templates/home.html:153
msgid ""
"Join a community of ambitious and committed women from around the world."
msgstr ""
"Rejoignez une communauté de femmes ambitieuses et engagées du monde entier."

#: templates/home.html:159
msgid "Entrepreneurship"
msgstr "Entrepreneuriat"

#: templates/home.html:160
msgid ""
"Let's celebrate women entrepreneurs and their initiatives that are "
"transforming our societies."
msgstr ""
"Célébrons les femmes entrepreneures et leurs initiatives qui transforment "
"nos sociétés."

#: templates/home.html:166
msgid "African Diaspora"
msgstr "Diaspora Africaine"

#: templates/home.html:167
msgid ""
"A bridge between Africa and its diaspora to share, learn, and collaborate."
msgstr ""
"Un pont entre l'Afrique et sa diaspora pour partager, apprendre et "
"collaborer."

#: templates/home.html:181
msgid "Join a community of inspiring women"
msgstr "Rejoignez une communauté de femmes inspirantes"

#: templates/home.html:182
msgid ""
"Exchange ideas, share your experiences and develop your projects with women "
"from all over the world."
msgstr ""
"Échangez des idées, partagez vos expériences et développez vos projets avec "
"des femmes du monde entier."

#: templates/home.html:271
msgid "Our services"
msgstr "Nos services"

#: templates/home.html:276
msgid "Featured"
msgstr "Mise en avant"

#: templates/home.html:277
msgid "We highlight women and their projects through our platforms."
msgstr ""
"Nous mettons en lumière les femmes et leurs projets à travers nos "
"plateformes."

#: templates/home.html:283
msgid "Interviews &amp; portraits"
msgstr "Interviews & portraits"

#: templates/home.html:284
msgid ""
"Authentic stories to inspire and motivate everyone who reads Lioness, the "
"magazine for queens."
msgstr ""
"Des histoires authentiques pour inspirer et motiver quiconque lit Lioness, "
"le magazine des reines."

#: templates/home.html:290
msgid "Accompaniement"
msgstr "Accompagnement"

#: templates/home.html:291
msgid ""
"If you become a member, you will have access to resources, advice, and tools "
"to boost your business."
msgstr ""
"En devenant membre, vous aurez accès à des ressources, des conseils et des "
"outils pour booster votre activité."

#: templates/home.html:297
msgid "Media Conten"
msgstr "Média & Contenu"

#: templates/home.html:298
msgid ""
"If you become a member, you'll have access to podcasts, videos, and articles "
"to learn and grow."
msgstr ""
"En devenant membre, vous aurez accès à des podcasts, des vidéos et des "
"articles pour apprendre et grandir."

#: templates/home.html:334
msgid "is a publication of Layilab."
msgstr "est une publication de Layilab."

#: templates/home.html:393
msgid "Service"
msgstr "Service"

#: templates/home.html:394
msgid "The Most Impactful Personalities"
msgstr "Les Personnalités les Plus Impactantes"

#: templates/home.html:399
msgid ""
"Become a member of the community that celebrates women worldwide. Together, "
"we are breaking down patriarchal stereotypes."
msgstr ""
"Devenez membre de la communauté qui célèbre les femmes à travers le monde. "
"Ensemble, nous brisons les stéréotypes patriarcaux."
